# Frontend Rules

## Architecture

Use:
- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Ant Design
- React Router
- TanStack Query
- Axios
- dayjs

Do not add Redux in V1 unless explicitly requested.

## Folder structure

Use feature-based structure:

features/{feature}/
- {feature}Api.ts
- {feature}Types.ts
- {feature}Queries.ts
- pages/
- components/

## API rules

- Do not call Axios directly inside page components.
- Configure Axios only in api/httpClient.ts.
- Feature API files call httpClient.
- TanStack Query hooks call feature API files.

## TanStack Query rules

- Use useQuery for list/detail.
- Use useMutation for create/update/cancel actions.
- Invalidate related queries after mutation.
- Do not over-optimize cache in V1.

After payment create/cancel, invalidate:
- invoice list/detail
- payment list
- debt report
- dashboard summary
- recent payments

## Ant Design rules

Use Table for:
- lists
- reports
- debt
- payments
- invoices
- attendance

Use Form + Modal for:
- create/edit
- enroll student
- create payment
- cancel payment
- change package

Use Card/Statistic for:
- dashboard
- statistics

Use Tabs for:
- detail pages
- statistics
- reports

Use Tag for status.

## Naming

Pages:
- StudentListPage.tsx
- StudentDetailPage.tsx
- DashboardPage.tsx

Components:
- StudentFormModal.tsx
- InvoiceTable.tsx
- PaymentFormModal.tsx
- StatusTag.tsx

API:
- studentApi.ts
- paymentApi.ts

Types:
- studentTypes.ts
- paymentTypes.ts

Queries:
- studentQueries.ts
- paymentQueries.ts

