## Money display

Use MoneyText component.
Display with thousand separators.
Do not perform critical money calculations in frontend.

## Backend sync

When backend DTO changes:
- update frontend types
- update feature API
- update affected page/component
- update query invalidation if needed

Do not invent frontend statuses.
